verbose_text: A recent investigation of the expression levels and role of AQPs in patients with chronic otitis media (COM) with otorrhea, published in Clinical and Experimental Otorhinolaryngology by Kim et al. [XREF_BIBR], found that the mRNAs of AQPs 1-6, 8, and 10 were expressed in inflammatory tissue obtained from patients with COM, with or without otorrhea.
